screen_description: SDL screen of empty GAL1p vector. A donor strain (W8164-2C) was used to pair an empty vector (pWJ1781) to the MATalpha KanMX gene disruption collection.
SDL screen of galactose induced overexpression of AIM25. A donor strain (W8164-2C) was used to pair GAL1p-AIM25 (pWJ2083) to the MATalpha KanMX gene disruption collection.
SDL screen of galactose induced overexpression of AKR2. A donor strain (W8164-2C) was used to pair GAL1p-AKR2 (pWJ2081) to the MATalpha KanMX gene disruption collection.
SDL screen of galactose induced overexpression of BUR6. A donor strain (W8164-2C) was used to pair GAL1p-BUR6 (pWJ2082) to the MATalpha KanMX gene disruption collection.
